---
// Mentoring — EN (dark theme)
import MarketingLayout from "../../layouts/MarketingLayout.astro";
---

<MarketingLayout title="Mentoring" description="Season-long hockey development program with dedicated mentors. Video review, skill skates, exercise plans, nutrition, mental skills, and academic support.">

  <section class="mpg-hero">
    <div class="mpg-container">
      <p class="mpg-hero__eyebrow">Service</p>
      <h1 class="mpg-hero__title">Mentoring</h1>
      <p class="mpg-hero__lead">Rise Advancement's mentoring program pairs every player with a dedicated mentor for the season. You choose the services that fit your game and your goals. Every engagement starts with an onboarding session, goal-setting, and regular check-ins throughout.</p>
      <a href="mailto:riseadvancements@gmail.com?subject=Mentoring - Inquiry" class="hp-btn-primary"><span>Get Started</span></a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <div class="hp-divider"><div class="hp-divider__puck"></div></div>

  <section class="mpg-section mpg-surface">
    <div class="mpg-container">
      <div class="mpg-header-center">
        <div class="mpg-label">Process</div>
        <h2 class="mpg-heading">How It Works</h2>
        <p class="mpg-subtitle">From day one, our mentors are in your corner.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="mpg-steps mpg-steps--4">
        <div class="mpg-step">
          <div class="mpg-step__number">1</div>
          <h3>Plan</h3>
          <p>You'll start with a planning session to map out the season, set clear goals, and decide which services make the most sense for where you are in your development.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="mpg-step">
          <div class="mpg-step__number">2</div>
          <h3>Choose</h3>
          <p>Pick what fits. All services can be delivered virtually unless noted.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="mpg-step">
          <div class="mpg-step__number">3</div>
          <h3>Check-ins</h3>
          <p>Your mentor stays connected throughout, tracking progress, making adjustments, and giving you direct, honest feedback.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="mpg-step">
          <div class="mpg-step__number">4</div>
          <h3>Wrap</h3>
          <p>Exit interview. What worked, what's next.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <div class="hp-divider"><div class="hp-divider__puck"></div></div>

  <section class="mpg-section">
    <div class="mpg-container">
      <div class="mpg-header-center">
        <h2 class="mpg-heading">Available Services</h2>
        <p class="mpg-subtitle">Pick what fits. All services can be delivered virtually unless noted.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="mpg-services-list">
        <div class="mpg-service-item"><h3>Weekly Check-ins</h3><p>Regular touchpoints with your mentor throughout the season covering progress, challenges, and adjustments to your plan. Included with every engagement.</p></div>
        <div class="mpg-service-item"><h3>Video Review</h3><p>One-on-one virtual game review with your mentor. Specific, actionable feedback on game or practice footage you can apply immediately.</p></div>
        <div class="mpg-service-item"><h3>Skill Skates</h3><p>In-person on-ice sessions focused on skating mechanics, puck handling, shooting, and position-specific skills with your Rise mentor.</p></div>
        <div class="mpg-service-item"><h3>Exercise Plan</h3><p>Structured off-ice training built around your position and goals. Updated regularly and delivered with full workout instructions.</p></div>
        <div class="mpg-service-item"><h3>Mental Skills</h3><p>Sessions with a professional mental skills coach covering focus, confidence, pressure management, and competitive mindset.</p></div>
        <div class="mpg-service-item"><h3>Nutritional Plan</h3><p>A custom nutrition plan built for your body and training load, designed to support performance and recovery all season long.</p></div>
        <div class="mpg-service-item"><h3>Stretching & Yoga</h3><p>Guided sessions focused on athletic performance, injury prevention, and recovery. Tailored to your schedule.</p></div>
        <div class="mpg-service-item"><h3>School Help</h3><p>Academic support for players balancing a demanding school schedule alongside hockey. Available throughout the season.</p></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <div class="hp-divider"><div class="hp-divider__puck"></div></div>

  <section class="mpg-section mpg-surface">
    <div class="mpg-container mpg-container--narrow">
      <div class="mpg-header-center">
        <h2 class="mpg-heading">Why It Works</h2>
      </div>
      <div class="mpg-checklist">
        <div class="mpg-checklist__item"><span class="mpg-checklist__check">&#10003;</span><span>Dedicated mentors who know your game</span></div>
        <div class="mpg-checklist__item"><span class="mpg-checklist__check">&#10003;</span><span>Flexible, build the program around your needs</span></div>
        <div class="mpg-checklist__item"><span class="mpg-checklist__check">&#10003;</span><span>24/7 response time from the mentorship team</span></div>
        <div class="mpg-checklist__item"><span class="mpg-checklist__check">&#10003;</span><span>Real feedback, real accountability, all season long</span></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <div class="hp-divider"><div class="hp-divider__puck"></div></div>

  <section class="mpg-section">
    <div class="mpg-container mpg-container--narrow">
      <div class="mpg-header-center">
        <h2 class="mpg-heading">Who Is It For?</h2>
      </div>
      <p class="mpg-who">Mentoring is available to elite players at any level and to players who are looking for ongoing support in their new environment. Programs are built individually; no two are the same.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <div class="hp-divider"><div class="hp-divider__puck"></div></div>

  <section class="mpg-section">
    <div class="mpg-container mpg-container--narrow">
      <div class="mpg-header-center">
        <h2 class="mpg-heading">Questions</h2>
      </div>
      <div class="mpg-faq__list">
        <div class="mpg-faq-item"><h3>Can I pick individual services?</h3><p>Yes. That's the whole point.</p></div>
        <div class="mpg-faq-item"><h3>How often are check-ins?</h3><p>Weekly.</p></div>
        <div class="mpg-faq-item"><h3>What if my kid is struggling?</h3><p>We adjust the plan and support them through it.</p></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <nav class="mpg-service-nav">
    <a href="/services/the-move">The Move</a>
    <a href="/services/mentoring" class="active">Mentoring</a>
    <a href="/services/hk-program">HK Program</a>
    <a href="/why-us">Why RISE</a>
  </nav>

  <section class="mpg-cta">
    <div class="mpg-container" style="text-align: center;">
      <h2>Ready to start developing?</h2>
      <div class="mpg-cta__buttons">
        <a href="mailto:riseadvancements@gmail.com?subject=Mentoring - Inquiry" class="hp-btn-white">Email Us</a>
        <a href="https://wa.me/85290950387" class="hp-btn-ghost">WhatsApp</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

</MarketingLayout>
